Additional minor Oscilloscope enhancements (#6629)

* Fix parts of the oscilloscope floating if there's noise.

Should always be anchored at -100dB now.

* Reduce the default and minimum sizes of the oscilloscope.

Response to user feedback.

* Add keyboard shortcut Alt+O for toggling the oscilloscope.

* Fix description of right-channel button in Oscilloscope.

* Set channel selection to off in the destructor.